---
title: Pan-Seared Chicken with Roasted Potatoes, Green Beans, and Creamy Dill Sauce
description: We’ve cracked the code to creating crowd-pleasing dinners, sauce! Everyone loves a creamy sauce draped over juicy chicken, steak, or pork chops. This sauce is spiked with a touch of mustard and fresh dill for brightness.
